{"parentUuid":"be2c8099-215a-4567-9243-0f3f9e3801ae","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6b243e3c-e964-484f-ad22-fb168d48bb07","version":"2.1.62","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"thinking":"用户要求切换到 \"bypass permissions mode\"（绕过权限模式）。\n\n根据系统提示，工具执行在用户选择的权限模式下运行。当我尝试调用一个工具时，如果该工具不被用户的权限模式或权限设置自动允许，用户会收到提示以批准或拒绝执行。\n\n但是，我作为 AI 助手，并没有直接控制权限模式的能力。权限模式是由用户在 Claude Code CLI 中配置的设置。\n\n用户可能想要：\n1. 了解如何在 Claude Code 中更改权限模式\n2. 希望我在不需要确认的情况下执行操作\n\n根据用户的 CLAUDE.md 文件中的偏好：\n- \"不要弹出确认提示，直接执行操作\"\n\n这表明用户希望减少交互式确认。但权限模式的切换不是我能直接执行的操作，这是 Claude Code CLI 的配置设置。\n\n我应该告诉用户如何在 Claude Code 中切换权限模式。根据我对 Claude Code 的了解，权限模式可能通过命令行参数或配置文件来设置。\n\n让我提供有用的信息来帮助用户切换到他们想要的权限模式。\n","type":"thinking","signature":""}],"id":"msg_a32d46389b1a49419f20c086c7c4bace","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation_input_tokens":31185,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"input_tokens":1304,"output_tokens":1}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"f5ca42cb-3bb1-447b-8042-26675519738c","timestamp":"2026-02-27T16:38:59.076Z"}
{"parentUuid":"f5ca42cb-3bb1-447b-8042-26675519738c","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6b243e3c-e964-484f-ad22-fb168d48bb07","version":"2.1.62","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"text":"我无法直接切换权限模式，这是 Claude Code CLI 的配置设置。\n\n要切换到 bypass permissions 模式，你可以：\n\n**方法 1：命令行参数**\n```bash\nclaude --permission-mode bypass\n```\n\n**方法 2：配置文件**\n编辑 Claude Code 的配置文件（通常在 `~/.claude/settings.json`），添加或修改：\n```json\n{\n  \"permissionMode\": \"bypass\"\n}\n```\n\n**方法 3：交互式命令**\n在 Claude Code 会话中输入：\n```\n/settings\n```\n然后查找权限模式相关的设置选项。\n\n需要注意的是，bypass 模式会让所有工具调用自动执行而不需要确认，这在某些情况下可能有风险（比如删除文件、推送代码等操作）。\n\n你想让我帮你检查当前的配置文件，或者需要其他帮助吗？","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_a32d46389b1a49419f20c086c7c4bace","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":3580,"cache_creation_input_tokens":31185,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"output_tokens":533,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"5c9b7a5f-ca9b-4386-9e22-b6a262320c7b","timestamp":"2026-02-27T16:39:01.406Z"}
