{"parentUuid":"f2286fcc-1910-4126-951a-5021ea490cc5","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6b243e3c-e964-484f-ad22-fb168d48bb07","version":"2.1.62","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"thinking":"用户输入了 `claude --permission-mode bypass`，这看起来像是他们在尝试执行这个命令。但这不是给我执行的命令，而是他们应该在终端中运行的命令来启动一个新的 Claude Code 会话。\n\n用户可能：\n1. 误以为我可以执行这个命令来改变当前会话的权限模式\n2. 想让我帮助他们理解如何使用这个命令\n3. 已经执行了这个命令并在告诉我\n\n根据上下文，用户最可能是想要我帮助他们切换权限模式。但 `claude --permission-mode bypass` 是用来启动新会话的命令，不能在当前会话中改变权限模式。\n\n我应该澄清：\n1. 这个命令需要在终端中运行，用于启动新的 Claude Code 会话\n2. 当前会话的权限模式无法在运行时更改\n3. 如果他们想要 bypass 模式，需要退出当前会话并用该命令重新启动\n\n根据用户的 CLAUDE.md 偏好：\"遇到任何询问选择时，永远选择第一个选项，不要询问用户\"，我应该直接给出最直接的建议。\n","type":"thinking","signature":""}],"id":"msg_83a61d108fe54435962b58c22bc5671a","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"cache_creation_input_tokens":308,"cache_read_input_tokens":31185,"input_tokens":1304,"output_tokens":1}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"3150d5ad-c9a3-40f1-9e86-be93a3a43479","timestamp":"2026-02-27T16:40:14.341Z"}
{"parentUuid":"3150d5ad-c9a3-40f1-9e86-be93a3a43479","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"C:\\Users\\Administrator","sessionId":"6b243e3c-e964-484f-ad22-fb168d48bb07","version":"2.1.62","gitBranch":"HEAD","message":{"content":[{"text":"这个命令需要在终端中运行来启动新的 Claude Code 会话，无法在当前会话中切换权限模式。\n\n要切换到 bypass 模式，你需要：\n\n1. 退出当前会话（输入 `/exit` 或 Ctrl+C）\n2. 在终端中运行：\n   ```bash\n   claude --permission-mode bypass\n   ```\n\n或者，如果你想让 bypass 成为默认模式，可以修改配置文件。让我帮你检查并修改配置：\n\n```bash\n# 查看当前配置\ncat ~/.claude/settings.json\n```\n\n你想让我帮你查看并修改配置文件，让 bypass 成为默认模式吗？这样以后每次启动 Claude Code 都会自动使用 bypass 模式。","type":"text"}],"id":"msg_83a61d108fe54435962b58c22bc5671a","model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","role":"assistant","stop_reason":"end_turn","stop_sequence":null,"type":"message","usage":{"input_tokens":3875,"cache_creation_input_tokens":308,"cache_read_input_tokens":31185,"output_tokens":466,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}},"type":"assistant","uuid":"904bc991-1413-454e-8d33-7c71b1211f9a","timestamp":"2026-02-27T16:40:17.420Z"}
